If you're using Firefox, just press SHIFT+F2 to open a console at the bottom, then type "cookie set gog_lc GB_EUR_en" (without the quotes). Reload.

You can now buy all "banned" games on GOG. The change is permanent, so feel free to switch the site language back to German if you want...
-- https://www.gog.com/forum/general/a_sad_german/post17
